Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.33,Default,K,0,0,0,,Koikawa Shungiku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.46,mushibugyo_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,恋川春菊君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.05,mushibugyo_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,九十九の人斬りといわれた
